{"tid":2494032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"足總唔記得book 場 港超冇得踢","createTime":"2021-04-18T10:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T11:37:01.000Z","uid":7376,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5309fb934396bf8c6771216bf41ba865241d8133","tid":2494032,"uid":7376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢啦#HKFA<br />\n<br />\n周日（18日）一場港甲賽事因球場問題而被迫擇日再賽！據讀者消息指，事緣原定周日（18日）下午3時半，於馬鞍山遊樂場舉行之港甲賽事永義地產對和富大埔，因雙方球員和足總工作人員到場才得知球場早已被公眾人士預訂。<br />\n<br />\n經一輪溝通後，雙方職、球員和足總人員決定移師馬鞍山運動場比賽，惟因有球隊未有準備真草場球鞋，令賽事被迫擇日再賽，無不令涉事球隊及球迷感相當無奈！<br />\n<br />\n足總現時在官網上顯示球賽於馬鞍山運動場進行，惟據消息人士指，賽前不論雙方球員、球迷均根據網頁資料而前往馬鞍山遊樂場，換言之在事件發生後，足總才更改網頁資料，引致今次「蝦碌」事件。"},{"pid":"901ab9a69fbbf6a3d2f3ea27c15b7bde1e080cdb","tid":2494032,"uid":4206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"港甲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0e54888ae14e5437b380edcb788deb1637591e","tid":2494032,"uid":7376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"901ab9a69fbbf6a3d2f3ea27c15b7bde1e080cdb","tid":2494032,"uid":4206,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"港甲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:58:31.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8eda1919faa8b8e4ac15baa52db5c3dea39f4c","tid":2494032,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"港超定港甲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1526fe516127cade2958b4da1dd9b86bc4c1fc","tid":2494032,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:37:01.000Z","msg":"On9執柒咗佢啦"}]}